      </Comment>
    </Member>
    <Member Name="lr_Velocity" Datatype="LReal">
      <Comment>
        <MultiLanguageText Lang="en-US">MOVE: path velocity [mm/s]</MultiLanguageText>
      </Comment>
    </Member>
    <Member Name="i16_BufferMode" Datatype="Int">
      <Comment>
        <MultiLanguageText Lang="en-US">MOVE: MC_MoveLinearAbsolute BufferMode for this command -- 1 = stop at this point (BM_BUFFERED), 5 = blend through it (BM_BLENDING_HIGH). Never 0 (MC_Aborting is invalid for a kinematic path -&gt; 16#80B2).</MultiLanguageText>
      </Comment>
    </Member>
    <Member Name="lr_DwellMs" Datatype="LReal">
      <Comment>
        <MultiLanguageText Lang="en-US">GRIPPER: grip/release settle hold time [ms]</MultiLanguageText>
      </Comment>
    </Member>
    <Member Name="bo_GripperGrip" Datatype="Bool">
      <Comment>
        <MultiLanguageText Lang="en-US">GRIPPER: level value written to GDB_Control.bo_gripperGrip</MultiLanguageText>
      </Comment>
    </Member>
    <Member Name="bo_GripperRelease" Datatype="Bool">
      <Comment>
        <MultiLanguageText Lang="en-US">GRIPPER: if TRUE, pulse GDB_Control.bo_gripperRelease for the dwell then drop it</MultiLanguageText>
      </Comment>
    </Member>
    <Member Name="bo_IsBoxEnd" Datatype="Bool">
      <Comment>
        <MultiLanguageText Lang="en-US">MOVE: TRUE on the PLACE_RETRACT move that completes a box -- increments statBoxesPlaced and re-arms the spawn request</MultiLanguageText>
      </Comment>
    </Member>
    <Member Name="i16_HmiStep" Datatype="Int">
      <Comment>
        <MultiLanguageText Lang="en-US">Value published to GDB_PalletizingCmd.i16_PalletStep when this command becomes active -- preserves the HMI 1..48 step display</MultiLanguageText>
      </Comment>
    </Member>
